A vintage 1960s-style illustration of a crystal ball sitting on an ornate wooden desk, surrounded by scattered punch cards and early computer printouts. Inside the glowing amber crystal ball, swirling abstract patterns of data streams and geometric shapes form mysterious configurations. The scene has warm sepia tones with touches of deep burgundy and gold, rendered in a mid-century advertising illustration style with visible brush textures and halftone dots. A curious magnifying glass rests nearby, catching the light from the crystal's glow.
